, Inebilizumab, More', 'Sunitinib, Regorafenib, Midostaurin, Copanlisib, Lenvatinib, Erlotinib, Abemaciclib, Trametinib, Vandetanib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Alectinib', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/77147/', '[1] "Product Information. Turalio (pexidartinib)." Daiichi Sankyo, Inc., Parsippany, NJ.[2] "Product Information. Turalio (pexidartinib)." Daiichi Sankyo, Inc., Parsippany, NJ.', 1767369485);
